--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ef4120e8d7cc4784ba80e7aeb2d6d58d, type: 3}
  m_Name: Muninn_Dialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  Repeatable: 0
  Lines:
  - Text: You have broken the first chain and now plan to follow through on the second
      one, is that so? You really are a beast rampaging. You ought to be bound, too.
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: df199855e161c314d94e5812fb871b01, type: 2}
  - Text: You are a lot ruder than the other one; I am no beast.
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8b9b771dc2f105a40a7ee49c43e5d895, type: 2}
  - Text: Yet you seek to destroy our world, quite beast-like of you, even if you
      have a smart mouth on yourself.
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: df199855e161c314d94e5812fb871b01, type: 2}
  - Text: "You also peddle this lie of the world\u2019s destruction; he is my father
      and Asgard has punished my siblings for no reason, then when he seeks an eye
      for an eye you torture him just as well."
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8b9b771dc2f105a40a7ee49c43e5d895, type: 2}
  - Text: Does that not make you the beasts?
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8b9b771dc2f105a40a7ee49c43e5d895, type: 2}
  - Text: You speak confidently of what you do not comprehend, beast. Face the trial
      and destroy the world.
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: df199855e161c314d94e5812fb871b01, type: 2}
  OnFinished:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
